snippet.title: Amber Heard Audio Tapes Shed New Light--On EVERYTHING!
snippet.description:
Audio tapes have surfaced where Amber Heard admitted to hitting Johnny Depp.  Not only that, but she taunted him for pointing out that he was abused by her!  So I'm just weighing in on that whole situation.  There are two videos to recommend here too, which I'll link.  Anyway, this is a short but hopefully informative video about what I think we can expect from all this revelations. Thank you for watching!  I'll be back soon.
